 8:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='519000' id='t-519000'>Now, a completely different thought.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='523000' id='t-523000'>I'm always imagining myself in different situations.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='527000' id='t-527000'>I'm imagining myself as a machine.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529000' id='t-529000'>What would I love?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531000' id='t-531000'>I would love to be bathed in oil.</span>
