 9:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='584000' id='t-584000'>From an engineering point of view,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587000' id='t-587000'>this is just a little four-bar linkage.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='589000' id='t-589000'>And then again, this is a found object, a little fan that I found.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594000' id='t-594000'>And I thought, what about the gesture of opening the fan,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597000' id='t-597000'>and how simply could I state something.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600000' id='t-600000'>And, in a case like this, I'm trying to make something which is clear</span>
