<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615000' id='t-615000'>For me, the process is very important,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620000' id='t-620000'>because I'm inventing machines,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622000' id='t-622000'>but I'm also inventing tools to make machines,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625000' id='t-625000'>and the whole thing is all sort of wrapped up from the beginning.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='628000' id='t-628000'>So this is a little wire-bending tool.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>After many years of bending gears with a pair of pliers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='634000' id='t-634000'>I made that tool, and then I made this other tool</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='637000' id='t-637000'>for sort of centering gears very quickly --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>sort of developing my own little world of technology.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644000' id='t-644000'>My life completely changed when I found a spot welder.</span>
