11:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>And that was that tool.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='653000' id='t-653000'>It completely changed what I could do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655000' id='t-655000'>Now here, I'm going to do a very poor job of silver soldering.</span>
