<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665000' id='t-665000'>I just like, throw it in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='667000' id='t-667000'>I mean, real jewelers put little bits of solder in.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='670000' id='t-670000'>So, that's a finished gear.</span>
