<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674000' id='t-674000'>When I moved to Boston,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676000' id='t-676000'>I joined a group called the World Sculpture Racing Society.</span>
