11:33
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='682000' id='t-682000'>And the idea, their premise was that we wanted to show</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689000' id='t-689000'>pieces of sculpture on the street,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='691000' id='t-691000'>and there'd be no subjective decision about what was the best.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695000' id='t-695000'>It would be -- whatever came across the finish line first would be the winner.</span>
