11:49
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='698000' id='t-698000'>So I made -- this is my first racing sculpture,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>and I thought, &quot;Oh, I'm going to make a cart,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>and I'm going to have it --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>I'm going to have my hand writing 'faster,'</span>
